{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"177aa2acc2","title":"江青致王洪文叶剑英张春桥邓小平陈锡联苏振华的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"104043d12d","index":0,"year":1974,"month":1,"day":28,"articleId":"177aa2acc2"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"6f7a683373","name":"军队和军事","type":"主题"},{"id":"82305e518c","name":"江青","type":"人物"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"ff3246377b","name":"批陈整风和批林批孔","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"jqjianghua","name":"江青十年讲话汇编","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"/books/jqjianghua.pdf"},{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"421124ccd3","name":"江青"}]},"publication_details":{"jqjianghua":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"1355621fb6","type":"title","text":"江青致王洪文叶剑英张春桥邓小平陈锡联苏振华的信","index":0,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"177aa2acc2"},{"id":"e7e4c91e1f","type":"paragraph","text":"洪文、剑英、春桥、小平、锡联、振华同志，请转世友、紫阳同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"177aa2acc2"},{"id":"c7a2c488b7","type":"paragraph","text":"请代我向广州军区全体指战员，海南岛，西沙群岛全体军民，同志们致以无产阶级革命的敬礼！祝贺西沙群岛全军，民兵，渔民同志们与敌周旋，取得维护祖国主权的伟大胜利。","index":2,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"177aa2acc2"},{"id":"781a7ec7f5","type":"paragraph","text":"我身在北京，心逐南海汹涌澎拜，虽不能与同志们一块持枪战斗，但在思想上，政治上正在进行着一场大斗争。这场斗争是大是大非，是路线斗争，是在以毛主席为首的党中央直接领导下，在上层建筑，意识形态领域中进行一场持久的斗争──批林批孔运动正向纵深发展，势若燎原。我们是心连心的，我们都要打倒帝修反，为建设社会主义的新中国，各自在党分配的岗位上战斗着，为了表示我对同志们的祝贺，特请作家浩然同志，诗人张永枚同志，记者蒋豪济同志代表我前去看望坚持在前线的英雄们并送给你们","index":3,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"177aa2acc2"},{"id":"0b2853245c","type":"paragraph","text":"──《林彪与孔孟之道》500份","index":4,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"177aa2acc2"},{"id":"5f73b92909","type":"paragraph","text":"──《五四以来反动派和地主资产阶级学者尊孔言论辑录》500份","index":5,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"177aa2acc2"},{"id":"8ea8c5bb16","type":"paragraph","text":"──《批林批孔材料（一），（二）》各 500份","index":6,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"177aa2acc2"},{"id":"c720314427","type":"paragraph","text":"──《鲁迅批判孔孟之道言论摘录》500份","index":7,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"177aa2acc2"},{"id":"82699ab7b0","type":"paragraph","text":"学习的第一单元是毛主席《我的一点意见》，第二单元是《毛主席致江青同志的一封信》，第三单元是《毛主席视察南方时和沿途负责同志的谈话》以上三份文件请世友，紫阳同志为你们准备。中央的通知还会告诉你们其他读物。","index":8,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"177aa2acc2"},{"id":"dfd44f5301","type":"paragraph","text":"致","index":9,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"177aa2acc2"},{"id":"4912768b19","type":"paragraph","text":"无产阶级革命的敬礼","index":10,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"177aa2acc2"},{"id":"1db5c987c0","type":"paragraph","text":"江青74.1.28凌晨 5时","index":11,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"177aa2acc2"}],"page":{"id":"8ad6181088","publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"177aa2acc2","start":688,"end":688}},"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"06daa44532","type":"paragraph","text":"──《五四以来反动派和地主资产阶级学者尊孔言论辑录》500份","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"177aa2acc2"},{"id":"18d7381e9e","type":"paragraph","text":"──《林彪与孔孟之道》500份","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"177aa2acc2"},{"id":"459d16ec0e","type":"paragraph","text":"74.1.28凌晨5时","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"177aa2acc2"},{"id":"738de43d3a","type":"paragraph","text":"──《批林批孔材料（一），（二）》各500份","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"177aa2acc2"},{"id":"8f8447327a","type":"paragraph","text":"致","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"177aa2acc2"},{"id":"965ddea793","type":"paragraph","text":"江青","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"177aa2acc2"},{"id":"9a2935549a","type":"paragraph","text":"学习的第一单元是毛主席《我的一点意见》，第二单元是《毛主席致江青同志的一封信》，第三单元是《毛主席视察南方时和沿途负责同志的谈话》以上三份文件请世友，紫阳同志为你们准备。中央的通知还会告诉你们其他读物。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"177aa2acc2"},{"id":"ab5ca32a88","type":"paragraph","text":"──《鲁迅批判孔孟之道言论摘录》500份","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"177aa2acc2"},{"id":"b472bb2d04","type":"paragrap